  <brief_title>Community Based Strategies to Reduce Maternal Mortality in Northern Nigeria</brief_title>
  <official_title>Strengthening the Midwife Service Scheme With Community Focused Interventions: Evidence From a Randomized Controlled Field Trial in Nigeria</official_title>
