    <intervention_name>Voluntary Health Worker (VHW) Program</intervention_name>
    <description>Voluntary Health Workers will conduct door-to-door campaigns on maternal and child health, and will visit pregnant women regularly to to educate and to encourage use of antenatal care and facility-based deliveries.</description>
